comments: Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in Jackson's (DET) path and does not deliver the contact.
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in Jackson's (DET) path and does not deliver the contact, some of which occurs to Jackson's side.
Plumlee's (DET) left hand is extended forward when marginal contact occurs with Tatum's (BOS) front at the end of the drive.
Plumlee (DET) and Brown (BOS) make incidental foot-to-foot contact with one another in the lane.
Williams (BOS) makes contact across Grant's (DET) face during his driving shot attempt.
Theis (BOS) sets the pick on Jackson (DET) and gives Jackson room to avoid the contact, which Theis does not deliver.
Plumlee (DET) firms up in his defensive position and absorbs the body contact made with Tatum (BOS) inside the perimeter.
Jackson (DET) and Theis (BOS) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Smart (BOS) is turning slightly as marginal body contact occurs with Rose (DET) during his driving shot attempt.
Williams (BOS) makes incidental contact with Grant's (DET) right arm as he simultaneously makes contact with the ball during rebounding.
Grant (DET) remains in-bounds and releases the ball before his momentum then takes him out of bounds.
Bey (DET) has his arm around Williams' (BOS) upper half and quickly slides it off.
Theis (BOS) firms up in his screening position in Grant's (DET) path and absorbs the contact.

Grant (DET) has his hand rested on Brown's (BOS) hip as Brown starts his upward shooting motion and quickly removes it without applying any force. Grant then makes incidental "high-five" contact with Brown after the release.
Prior to the timeout being awarded, Smart (BOS) reaches in and marginal contact occurs with Rose (DET) inside half-court.
Tatum (BOS) reflexively places his arm around Plumlee's (DET) upper half after the hand-off and quickly slides it off.
Plumlee (DET) makes clean contact with the ball before incidental contact occurs with Smart (BOS) thereafter during the rebound.
Williams (BOS) commits the take foul on Bey (DET).
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in Jackson's (DET) path and does not deliver the contact.
Theis (BOS) briefly has his hands on Plumlee's (DET) right arm and removes them as the ball falls toward the pair during rebounding.
Plumlee (DET) has his left forearm extended forward when marginal contact occurs with Smart's (BOS) front after his gather.
Smart (BOS) commits the take foul on Plumlee (DET).
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in Grant's (DET) path and absorbs the contact.
